eve Finch\n|\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Then She Found Me]]''\n| Ben Green\n|\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Bee Movie]]''\n| Adam Flayman (voice)\n|\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[Diminished Capacity]]''\n| Cooper Zerbs\n|\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[Finding Amanda]]''\n| Taylor Peters Mendon\n| \n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[The Tale of Despereaux (film)|The Tale of Despereaux]]''\n| [[Despereaux]] (voice)\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Wonderful World (2009 film)|Wonderful World]]''\n| Ben Singer\n|\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Margaret (2011 film)|Margaret]]''\n| John Van Tassel\n|\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Tower Heist]]''\n| Mr. Fitzhugh\n|\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[New Year's Eve (2011 film)|New Year's Eve]]''\n| Mr. Buellerton\n| Uncredited cameo\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Skum Rocks!]]''\n| Himself\n| Documentary\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Dirty Weekend (2015 film)|Dirty Weekend]]''\n| Les Moore\n|\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Trainwreck (film)|Trainwreck]]''\n| Himself\n| Cameo\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Manchester by the Sea (film)|Manchester by the Sea]]''\n| Jeffrey\n| \n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[The American Side]]''\n| Borden Chase\n|\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Rules Don't Apply]]''\n| Levar Mathis\n|\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[To Dust]]''\n| Albert\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Wonder Park]]''\n| Dad (voice)\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Love Is Blind (2019 film)|Love Is Blind]]''\n| Murray\n|\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Lazy Susan (film)|Lazy Susan]]''\n| Doug\n|\n|-\n| TBA\n| ''The Gettysburg Address''\n| Narrator (voice)\n| Documentary <br/>post-production\n|-\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Year !! Title !! Role !! Notes\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Lou Grant (TV series)|Lou Grant]]''\n| Mike\n| Television debut<br />Episode: \"Generations\"\n|-\n| 1985\n| ''[[List of Faerie Tale Theatre episodes#Season 4|Faerie Tale Theatre]]''\n| Prince Henry\n| Episode: \"Cinderella\"\n|-\n| 1985\n| ''[[Master Harold...and the Boys (1985 film)|Master Harold...and the Boys]]''\n| Hally Ballard\n| Television film\n|-\n| 1988, 1998\n| ''[[Saturday Night Live]]''\n| Himself (host)\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| 1993\n| ''[[A Life 