cing driver)|Michael Caine]]<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Tim Sugden]]\n|[[TVR Tuscan Speed 6|TVR Tuscan]] T400R\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{Dunlop}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 93\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Gearbox\n|-\n|[[TVR]] Speed Six 4.0L I6\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | 43<br>DNF\n| rowspan=\"2\" | GTS\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 66\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{flagicon|DEU}} [[Konrad Motorsport]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{flagicon|AUT}} [[Franz Konrad (racing driver)|Franz Konrad]]<br>{{flagicon|CHE}} Toni Seiler<br>{{flagicon|CHE}} [[Walter Brun]]\n|[[Saleen S7]]-R\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{Dunlop}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 91\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Gearbox\n|-\n|[[Ford Motor Company|Ford]] 7.0L V8\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | 44<br>DNF\n| rowspan=\"2\" | LMP900\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 21\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{flagicon|FRA}} Edouard Sezionale\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{flagicon|FRA}} Patrice Roussel<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} Edouard Sezionale<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} Lucas Lasserre\n| Norma M2000-2\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{Dunlop}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 82\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Engine\n|-\n|[[Ford Motor Company|Ford]] ([[Roush Fenway Racing|Roush]]) 6.0L V8\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | 45<br>DNF\n| rowspan=\"2\" | LMP675\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 31\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Courage Comp\u00e9tition]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{flagicon|FRA}} [[David Hallyday]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Philippe Alliot]]<br>{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Carl Rosenblad (racing driver)|Carl Rosenblad]]\n|[[Courage Comp\u00e9tition|Courage]] C65\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{Michelin}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 41\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Engine\n|-\n| JPX 3.4L V6\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | 46<br>DNF\n| rowspan=\"2\" | LMP900\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 10\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Audi]] Sport UK<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Arena Motorsport]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{flagicon|DEU}} [[Frank Biela]]<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Perry McCarthy]]<br>{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Mika Salo]]\n|[[Audi R8 (LMP)<!---Audi R8 race car may also refer to the LMS race car. The Audi R8 used in the 24 Hours of Le Mans is the LMP race car--->|Audi R8]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{Michelin}}\n| rows